 Unser Team kümmert sich innerhalb von 1-2 Werktagen um die Erstattung deiner Bestellung. Wir wünschen dir viel Freude bei deinem risikofreien Einkauf und der Pflege deiner Haare.</p><br><p>Deine Redaktion von Störtebekker</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="8801133f-e08f-4116-b22f-ac01e6493f21" class="r-1qtp09c"><div data-rid="96593a18-8cce-486b-bcff-b5a673fd712c" class="r-11dtysu"><div class="r-6b1xmj" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="2dfa82db-7171-4087-b87b-c94a68e8b788" class="r-1kj50rj"><div data-rid="d09a987f-8477-4980-91fa-df825f5094cd" class="r-1la37pi alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-7a85dd80-c0d4-4b38-bd6a-6ff2358ddaba-attributes-fontsize:28px;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-7a85dd80-c0d4-4b38-bd6a-6ff2358ddaba-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-7a85dd80-c0d4-4b38-bd6a-6ff2358ddaba-attributes-fontfamily:Figtree;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-7a85dd80-c0d4-4b38-bd6a-6ff2358ddaba-attributes-fontweight:undefined;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-7a85dd80-c0d4-4b38-bd6a-6ff2358ddaba-attributes-lineheight:36px;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-7a85dd80-c0d4-4b38-bd6a-6ff2358ddaba-attributes-letterspacing:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><h3><strong>Verlängerte 100 Tage Garantie</strong></h3></span></div><div data-rid="8f8da521-c6ca-45ba-af1c-93a2224cd5c0" class="r-1ycamd6 alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-6e12b10a-e026-4c86-adb6-5e9e500d0fd5-attributes-fontsize:20px;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-6e12b10a-e026-4c86-adb6-5e9e500d0fd5-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-styles-6e12b10a-e026-4c86-adb6-5e9e500d0fd5-attributes-fontfamily:Open Sans;--replo-library-9ab86cbe-1876-4689-a4ed-919dbad6b5c6-style